               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of the Savior of the World, መልክአ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡, Lamentations of the Virgin, ሰቆቃወ፡ ድንግል፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="12r" facs="002">Fols 1r–12r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3059RepCh339">Hymn to Jesus
                                                  Christ</title>
                     <incipit>ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘኢረከቡ፡ ተፍጻሚተ፡</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="12v" to="24v" facs="014">Fols 12v–24v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2285Saqoqa">Saqoqāwa
                                                  dǝngǝl</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
